Private Safaris & Tours To Asia-China




























1-888-561-5576
Award Winning Custom Tours








Kensington Tours












Private Guided Tours To China








Kensington Tours is an award winning tour company offering custom private guided safaris and tours at unbeatable value.

 Your Own Private Expert Guide & Vehicle
 Your Schedule, Your Budget, Your Preferences
 Private Tours for 20% Less Than Premium Group Tours


Most Popular Tours
Kensington Tours can customize any tour to your needs.  They offer private guided as well as small group tours.  Here are some samples of the most popular private tours:
Beijing, Xi'an & Shanghai Explorer
Beijing, Xi'an, Shanghai
8 days from $2,376 per person
Walk along the Great Wall, come face to face with the Terracotta Army, and visit ancient gardens and Buddhist temples. On this private guided tour, you’ll experience ancient and modern China at its absolute best. Complete with private guides, drivers, premium hotels, and more.
Highlights of China: Great Wall, Warriors, & Li River
Beijing, Xi'an, Yangshuo, Shanghai
9 days from $3,780 per person
Centuries fall away as you climb the Great Wall, look down upon the Terra Cotta Warriors, explore Tiananmen Square, and cruise the serene waters of the Li River. Voyage through China's must-see highlights with private guides and drivers at every stop.
China Highlights: Panda Adventure 
Beijing, Xi'an, Chengdu, Shanghai
10 days from $3,660 per person
Meet black-and-white celebrities at the famous panda research base in Chengdu. On this China adventure, you'll also experience the spellbinding highlights of Beijing, Xi'an and Shanghai. 
National Geographic Winning China Signature
Beijing, Xi'an, Longsheng, Yangshuo, Shanghai
12 days from $5,304 per person
This award winning tour presents the culture and beauty of China with private guide and exclusive access. Kids of all ages will love private tours of the Forbidden City, Great Wall, Temple of Heaven, Terra Cotta warriors, cooking with a local family, Li River cruise, bicycle tours, and much more!
Beijing, Shanghai and the Yangtze River in Style
Beijing, Yangtze River Cruise, Shanghai
9 days from $5,148 per person
Cruise the Yangze River and voyage through Beijing and Shanghai on this private guided journey fit for ancient emperors. Explore China's famed monuments and locations including the Forbidden City, spiritual temples & enchanting river gorges. 

Active China Adventure
Beijing, Xi'an, Longsheng, Yangshuo, Shanghai
12 days from $4,848 per person
Trek along the Great Wall, cycle to the famed Terra Cotta Warriors, hike around scenic rice paddies in Longsheng and much more on this active adventure. From Beijing to Shanghai you'll explore China's natural wonders and imperial legends with a private guide. 
Cities Of China In Style
Beijing, Xi'an, Shanghai, Hong Kong
10 days from $6,510 per person
Delve into the bygone dynasties of China in true style with this decadent 5* tour. Featuring starlit dinners, temples, palaces, cruises, gourmet feasts, cultural encounters, 1st class hotels, and chauffer. Expert private guides provide you with unparalleled insights and exclusive access.
Imperial Cities of China & Japan
Beijing, Xi'an, Shanghai, Tokyo, Kyoto
12 days from $6,912 per person
A tale of two countries. Embark on a dramatic & action packed odyssey through China and Japan's show-stopping cities & natural wonders.
Kingdoms of the Clouds
Beijing, Lhasa, Kathmandu
8 days from $4,448 per person
From the icy peaks of Everest to China's sprawling Great Wall, this all encompassing adventure has it all. Soar over Mount Everest in a plane, explore the palaces and temples of Durbar Square, walk along the Great Wall, explore the Forbidden City, and sleep in premium accommodations.




